Package: cosimmr
Type: Package
Title: A Package for Fast Fitting of Stable Isotope Mixing Models with Covariates
Version: 1.0
Date: 2024-04-25
Authors@R: c(person("Emma", "Govan", email = "emmagovan@gmail.com", role = c("cre","aut")),
          person("Andrew", "Parnell", role = "aut"))
Description: Fast fitting of Stable Isotope Mixing Models in R. It 
             allows for the inclusion of covariates. The package also has built-in summary functions
             and plot functions which allow for the creation of isospace plots.
License: GPL (>= 2)
